) (including genital field) L/W 432 / 305 , capitular bay L 81 ; W between outer margins of acetabular plates 181 ; acetabular plates fused with the postgenital sclerite; glandularia typically associated with genital field fused with the ventral shield; excretory pore fused with the postgenital sclerite. Palp (
